eu.linksmart.caf.cm.rules
Class Action

java.lang.Object
  eu.linksmart.caf.cm.rules.Action
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Action
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

An action defined as the RHS of a Rule, as part of a ContextRuleSet, to be installed in the Context Manager. The Context Manager should be able to handle the id of the Action given.

Attributes define the properties of the Action, for handling, whereas, the Parameters are expected to be particular to the processing of the Action

Author:
Michael Crouch
